"{\"uid\": \"scmp.com-news-hong-kong-politics-article-3280105-hong-kong-museum-showcase-olympic-medals-local-mainland-chinese-athletes\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Display at Museum of History part of exhibition marking anniversary of country's establishment, with Science Museum to also host exhibits  A new patriotic exhibition at the Hong Kong Museum of History will include medals won by local and mainland Chinese Olympians, as part of efforts to showcase the country's achievements and foster a sense of national identity among residents.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 101, \"end\": 115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_Science_Museum\", \"score\": 0.9999999973560989, \"rank\": 2.6439206560030378e-09, \"text\": \"Science Museum\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_Science_Museum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_Science_Museum\"}, {\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"score\": 0.9683123567861851, \"rank\": 0.03272444785985203, \"text\": \"mainland Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mainland_China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The venue in Tsim Sha Tsui, alongside the Hong Kong Science Museum, will host the \\\"Glorious Voyage: Splendid Achievements of the People's Republic of China in its 75 Years\\\" exhibition series.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_Science_Museum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hong Kong Science Museum\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_Science_Museum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_Science_Museum\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event has been organised to mark the 75th anniversary of the establishment of the People's Republic of China on October 1, which falls on Tuesday of next week.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking at Thursday's opening ceremony, Deputy Chief Secretary Warner Cheuk Wing-hing said the exhibition could help residents learn more about the country's various avenues of development.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warner_Music_Group\", \"score\": 0.5864601766632496, \"rank\": 0.5227269423787827, \"text\": \"Warner\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warner_Music_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warner_Music_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The exhibition can promote patriotic spirit to the public, \\\" he said, adding that it could also help to bolster patriotic education.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Secretary for Culture, Sports and Tourism Kevin Yeung Yun-hung earlier said that some museums would offer free admission as different government bureaus and departments rolled up their sleeves to prepare for the October 1 anniversary.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The exhibition includes 16 displays and brings together more than 170 images showcasing the nation's development and achievements.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1433, \"entities\": []}]}"